{"tid":210781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近有個減完肥既女仔搵返我,點算好","createTime":"2017-04-21T07:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T08:30:37.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f948e3ab7a767e2f46820c1fd83e7fd0a4e4906b","tid":210781,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"初初識佢個陣係好肥<br />\n其實又唔算係欣宜個種肥<br />\n但都算係肥架喇<br />\n<br />\n不過個陣我諗住識多個朋友冇咩所謂咁<br />\n都有keep住傾下日常野鳩up下咁<br />\n<br />\n後尾佢話因為讀書定唔知有意中人就少左聯絡<br />\n今朝見到佢wtsapp 同我say hi<br />\n我好有禮貌咁hi 返佢<br />\n點知佢問我得唔得閒食餐飯咁<br />\n見佢icon 瘦左好多<br />\n本來佢60kg 依家睇相應該得45左右<br />\n佢約左我聽晚出黎食飯<br />\n我唔知要準備咩好<br />\n有冇巴絲們俾下意見"},{"pid":"e5e50856b705aa80f25ffb90dc794bd72d11e1f1","tid":210781,"uid":73244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"套"},{"pid":"45a0305ca8475429418990929480ad5e300ca1cf","tid":210781,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dccb8baf772fefbb3d50bdc0b33e0279477d8df4","tid":210781,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"多女"},{"pid":"344e4471ced4bd93a0d335f2a82d6a9eaceb0710","tid":210781,"uid":92879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"準備填form做兵"},{"pid":"74f116dd4298700e1651b9fd8ee020488aeb9c97","tid":210781,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"c73408975cfbb682af1ba1e9690d0017e257aefa","tid":210781,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"45屌你非洲兒童?"},{"pid":"b710f504e543fa82a42a8a46bf862f3726cda3fa","tid":210781,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:17:29.000Z","msg":"問你借錢，一係問你借唔借錢"},{"pid":"200b98b08e6a653988d8ed6ecb7b6d259cb3c5e5","tid":210781,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy